{"tid":1626381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大馬首相籲林鄭辭職 恐六四在港重演","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:31:59.000Z","uid":51665,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f17a6a04fa2c9a9a148466bb403595997b521c1d","tid":1626381,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】馬來西亞首相馬哈蒂爾（Mahathir Mohamad，圖）昨日（4日）出席亞太法律協會（LawAsia）憲法及法治會議，在記者會被問及會給予香港行政長官林鄭月娥什麼建議時，他稱最好的做法是「辭職」，又稱中方最終或調派外來部隊鎮壓，在香港重演六四事件。<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾表示，香港的示威活動沒有減弱迹象，形容林鄭月娥陷於兩難。他說：「她要服從主人（masters），但同時她要自問良知；她的良知說香港民眾反對該法例（《逃犯條例》修訂）是對的，但她同時知道反修例的後果&hellip;&hellip;那在中國發生過，在天安門的事（指六四事件）&mdash;&mdash;示威民眾也是當區（北京）士兵的親友，故他們（中國政府）所做的是從其他地區帶進士兵，然後採取行動，即終結示威的嚴苛行動。我認為到最後，這就是中國會做的事，但對行政官員（林鄭月娥）來說，我認為最好是辭職。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20191005/s00001/1570214583176/%e5%a4%a7%e9%a6%ac%e9%a6%96%e7%9b%b8%e7%b1%b2%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7-%e6%81%90%e5%85%ad%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e6%bc%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191005%2Fs00001%2F1570214583176%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%259b%25b8%25e7%25b1%25b2%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7-%25e6%2581%2590%25e5%2585%25ad%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%25bc%2594&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrkyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=e666d961\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191005%2Fs00001%2F1570214583176%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%259b%25b8%25e7%25b1%25b2%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7-%25e6%2581%2590%25e5%2585%25ad%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%25bc%2594&h=2acc03b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20191005/s00001/1570214583176/%e5%a4%a7%e9%a6%ac%e9%a6%96%e7%9b%b8%e7%b1%b2%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7-%e6%81%90%e5%85%ad%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%a8%e6%b8%af%e9%87%8d%e6%bc%94</a><br />\n連大馬首相都收到風看來老解真的要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a017d8ec612679055d2de1f19220f031332b36","tid":1626381,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97f819633a8b9dce3e3b12dc71b83c682ff0ef06","tid":1626381,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭有良智？"},{"pid":"56d1aed235fd081a0477e72e844e2d2931766175","tid":1626381,"uid":199540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0a017d8ec612679055d2de1f19220f031332b36","tid":1626381,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"止蝕一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9e8871da9b514bf96773b05d61a82c905fab6c","tid":1626381,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0a017d8ec612679055d2de1f19220f031332b36","tid":1626381,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"諗多左岩岩先簽完5 G合作"},{"pid":"1be3b51ca6106d282092acdce45b3da2916f6a7a","tid":1626381,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"其實林鄭條臭老西以後點出去外訪？<br />\n邊個國家啋佢？<br />\n佢去到個個都笑9佢啦"}]}